Lets Make Sugar Free Nankhati 😋

Ingredients

1 cup maida
1/2 besan
1/4 suji
1 tsp baking soda
1 tsp elaichi powder
1/2 melted ghee
1/3 sweetify swetneer
Bake for 20min on low flame
